Package: meta-app
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Comprehensive Meta-Analysis App with Bivariate Support
Author: David Grabois
Maintainer: David Grabois <david.grabois@gmail.com>
Description: An interactive Shiny application for performing comprehensive meta-analyses, including fixed and random effects models, bivariate analysis with full OR and RR support, meta-regression with permutation tests, publication bias assessment, and sensitivity analysis. Features comprehensive statistical testing, forest plots, and influence analysis.
License: MIT
